00:13:15,698 --> 00:13:16,831
Hey!

250
00:13:16,964 --> 00:13:18,931
It would be faster
if you ride with me.

251
00:13:19,064 --> 00:13:21,131
We can settle things up later.

252
00:13:21,264 --> 00:13:23,331
Y'all might wanna
get going now.

253
00:13:23,464 --> 00:13:25,764
-But, Chief?
-What do you think you're--

254
00:13:25,898 --> 00:13:28,898
-[yelps]
-[boy] Where are you going?

255
00:13:34,864 --> 00:13:35,931
Uh-- Wh--

256
00:13:36,064 --> 00:13:38,864
[screaming]

257
00:13:40,264 --> 00:13:42,431
Aah!

258
00:13:45,264 --> 00:13:47,264
Ah. Ha-ha-ha!

259
00:13:50,364 --> 00:13:52,931
[Masaomi]
Oh, yeah? Thank God.

260
00:13:53,998 --> 00:13:55,664
No, I'm good for now.

261
00:13:55,798 --> 00:13:58,798
Sit tight. I'll call you
in a little while.

262
00:13:58,931 --> 00:13:59,898
Yeah.

263
00:14:00,031 --> 00:14:02,098
[phone beeps]

264
00:14:02,231 --> 00:14:03,464
[Chikage]
Your guys all safe?

265
00:14:03,598 --> 00:14:05,331
Yeah, just barely.

266
00:14:05,464 --> 00:14:06,898
-So?
-What?

267
00:14:07,031 --> 00:14:09,764
I might not look it,
but I'm a good listener.

268
00:14:09,898 --> 00:14:12,731
At least that's what all
my honeys keep telling me.

269
00:14:35,397 --> 00:14:37,031
It's running on instinct.

270
00:14:37,164 --> 00:14:40,497
Whatever consciousness
it had is gone.

271
00:14:43,831 --> 00:14:47,897
It seems it's lost all sanity
in this form as well.

272
00:14:48,031 --> 00:14:51,797
[thinking]
<i>How can I be sure</i>
<i>I will fight as before?</i>

273
00:14:51,931 --> 00:14:55,764
<i>Life in peace of city</i>
<i>does nothing but dull edge.</i>

274
00:14:56,697 --> 00:14:58,531
<i>Sloan tell me this.</i>

275
00:14:58,664 --> 00:15:01,497
How dare you question
my skill as fighter!

276
00:15:01,631 --> 00:15:03,131
Are you mocking me?

277
00:15:04,497 --> 00:15:06,097
<i>I deny it,</i>

278
00:15:06,231 --> 00:15:09,797
<i>but, in back of mind,</i>
<i>I knew truth.</i>

279
00:15:09,931 --> 00:15:12,397
<i>I did not mind</i>
<i>to be that way.</i>

280
00:15:12,531 --> 00:15:15,197
<i>Then, I meet man I try to kill</i>

281
00:15:15,331 --> 00:15:16,864
<i>but could not in end.</i>

282
00:15:16,997 --> 00:15:19,531
<i>He make me question values,</i>

283
00:15:19,664 --> 00:15:22,197
<i>lose sense of purpose.</i>

284
00:15:22,331 --> 00:15:24,797
<i>Shizuo Heiwajima.</i>

285
00:15:24,931 --> 00:15:27,631
<i>In days I spend</i>
<i>as trainee under Shizuo,</i>

286
00:15:27,764 --> 00:15:31,031
<i>I feel different kind of bliss</i>
<i>I never feel before.</i>

287
00:15:31,164 --> 00:15:34,997
<i>Nothing like bliss</i>
<i>of battle in past.</i>

288
00:15:35,131 --> 00:15:39,131
<i>I become aware of world</i>
<i>I have never known before.</i>

289
00:15:55,464 --> 00:15:57,897
<i>Then, Shizuo taken away.</i>

290
00:15:58,031 --> 00:16:01,497
<i>That was when</i>
<i>I receive new offer.</i>

291
00:16:01,631 --> 00:16:03,697
[vehicle beeping]

292
00:16:03,831 --> 00:16:09,831
<i>It was during attack</i>
<i>I have old feeling back again.</i>

293
00:16:12,431 --> 00:16:16,497
[people murmuring]

294
00:16:16,631 --> 00:16:20,431
<i>Longing for pursuit</i>
<i>of power return.</i>

295
00:16:21,331 --> 00:16:22,864
<i>I was almost convinced</i>

296
00:16:22,997 --> 00:16:25,931
<i>this world was world</i>
<i>I belong in.</i>

297
00:16:29,564 --> 00:16:30,731
Hey!

298
00:16:30,864 --> 00:16:32,331
[gasp]

299
00:16:32,464 --> 00:16:35,831
Varona. It's you, isn't it?

300
00:17:06,231 --> 00:17:08,631
[snarling]

301
00:17:14,631 --> 00:17:16,164
Even though
you're a monster,

302
00:17:16,297 --> 00:17:18,297
your goals are not
destruction and hate.

303
00:17:18,431 --> 00:17:22,297
You have
more important things
to pursue, don't you?

304
00:17:22,431 --> 00:17:24,497
I'm surprised
to be saying this,

305
00:17:24,631 --> 00:17:26,997
but I'm feeling
rather jealous.

306
00:17:49,031 --> 00:17:54,431
Uh, I guess she can
be stubborn, huh?

307
00:17:57,297 --> 00:18:00,831
[Varona]
<i>Shadow is most likely</i>
<i>Headless Rider.</i>

308
00:18:02,297 --> 00:18:05,497
<i>Why Kasane Kujiragi target it?</i>

309
00:18:05,631 --> 00:18:07,264
<i>Now I think of it,</i>

310
00:18:07,397 --> 00:18:10,231
<i>job did not come</i>
<i>from Jinnai Yodogiri.</i>

311
00:18:10,364 --> 00:18:13,031
<i>Offer come from Kasane.</i>

312
00:18:13,164 --> 00:18:16,464
<i>She give job</i>
<i>to fight monster.</i>

313
00:18:16,597 --> 00:18:19,297
<i>What would Sloan say</i>
<i>if were here?</i>

314
00:18:19,431 --> 00:18:21,931
<i>And what is wrong with man?</i>

315
00:18:22,064 --> 00:18:25,731
<i>Eyes are red.</i>
<i>Perhaps infected with virus.</i>

316
00:18:25,864 --> 00:18:29,697
<i>It possible Headless Rider</i>
<i>chasing man.</i>

317
00:18:29,831 --> 00:18:33,764
<i>Why? Are they enemies?</i>

318
00:18:33,897 --> 00:18:35,831
<i>Why would it hate him?</i>

319
00:18:37,031 --> 00:18:38,297
<i>Or...</i>

320
00:18:38,431 --> 00:18:40,797
<i>perhaps it in love with man.</i>

321
00:18:45,264 --> 00:18:46,731
<i>What is love?</i>

322
00:18:46,864 --> 00:18:49,031
<i>I have never loved anyone.</i>

323
00:18:49,164 --> 00:18:52,297
<i>It possible I do not</i>
<i>even love self.</i>

324
00:18:52,431 --> 00:18:54,831
<i>I am aware of concept,</i>

325
00:18:54,964 --> 00:18:58,197
<i>but am unsure if love</i>
<i>is required in life.</i>

326
00:18:58,331 --> 00:19:00,931
<i>It's not like air or food.</i>

327
00:19:02,397 --> 00:19:04,231
<i>Whatever case may be,</i>

328
00:19:04,364 --> 00:19:07,697
<i>this emotion called love</i>
<i>is not same as emotion</i>

329
00:19:07,831 --> 00:19:11,797
<i>I could feel during daily life</i>
<i>in peace of city.</i>

330
00:19:11,931 --> 00:19:15,831
<i>Is not same as feeling</i>
<i>during battle.</i>

331
00:19:15,964 --> 00:19:19,397
<i>I can no longer feel</i>
<i>that way again.</i>

332
00:19:19,531 --> 00:19:21,831
<i>Cover has been compromised.</i>

333
00:19:21,964 --> 00:19:25,497
<i>I have been seen by Shizuo.</i>

334
00:19:25,631 --> 00:19:28,831
By Shizuo?

335
00:19:28,964 --> 00:19:31,297
<i>I see now</i>
<i>what this loneliness,</i>

336
00:19:31,431 --> 00:19:35,964
<i>this desolation,</i>
<i>this sense of loss really is.</i>

337
00:19:37,231 --> 00:19:39,631
<i>I did not realize</i>
<i>how afraid I was</i>

338
00:19:39,764 --> 00:19:42,064
<i>to lose daily life in city.</i>

339
00:19:42,197 --> 00:19:43,564
<i>Now, I do.</i>

340
00:19:49,364 --> 00:19:51,531
<i>Nothing ever happen here.</i>

341
00:19:51,664 --> 00:19:53,131
<i>Is true.</i>

342
00:19:53,264 --> 00:19:55,364
<i>But, here, I find</i>
<i>what it mean to live</i>

343
00:19:55,497 --> 00:19:59,564
<i>and satisfaction that come</i>
<i>from peaceful existence.</i>

344
00:20:05,364 --> 00:20:07,531
<i>Is too late to turn back now.</i>

345
00:20:07,664 --> 00:20:10,064
<i>There is nothing I can do.</i>

346
00:20:11,864 --> 00:20:15,664
<i>I no longer have peaceful</i>
<i>daily life to return to.</i>

347
00:20:15,797 --> 00:20:17,564
<i>I am alone.</i>

348
00:20:19,464 --> 00:20:22,031
Goddamn it.

349
00:20:22,164 --> 00:20:23,764
Hmm?

350
00:20:24,764 --> 00:20:27,431
-[neighing]
-Is that Celty?

351
00:20:27,564 --> 00:20:32,031
-[men whimpering]
-[neighing]

352
00:20:32,164 --> 00:20:35,064
Hmm.

353
00:20:35,197 --> 00:20:38,897
Aren't you supposed
to be, uh, you know,

354
00:20:39,031 --> 00:20:40,631
Celty's bike?

355
00:20:42,964 --> 00:20:44,664
Where is she?

356
00:20:47,264 --> 00:20:49,831
You want me to get on you?

357
00:20:49,964 --> 00:20:53,264
Uh, I've never rode
a horse before.

358
00:20:53,397 --> 00:20:55,064
[nickering]

359
00:20:59,164 --> 00:21:00,631
[neighing]

360
00:21:00,764 --> 00:21:02,964
Sorry, I never learned how
to ride a motorbike, either.

361
00:21:06,631 --> 00:21:08,431
What do you want?

362
00:21:08,564 --> 00:21:11,097
Huh? Oh, this thing?

363
00:21:11,231 --> 00:21:14,431
Yeah, some punk-ass kid
gave it to me tonight.

364
00:21:14,564 --> 00:21:15,931
[gasp]

365
00:21:23,697 --> 00:21:25,064
[bike bell rings]

366
00:21:25,197 --> 00:21:27,964
Man, you're something else,
aren't you?

367
00:21:28,097 --> 00:21:32,664
Yeah, sure, this'll work.
I can ride one no swea--

368
00:21:36,164 --> 00:21:39,031
Let me guess.
Something happened
to Celty, didn't it?

369
00:21:39,164 --> 00:21:40,397
[bike bell ringing]

370
00:21:40,531 --> 00:21:43,164
All right.
Let's get going, then!

371
00:21:47,631 --> 00:21:48,864
[gasp]

372
00:21:51,164 --> 00:21:54,631
How's it going?
We haven't met before, I think.

373
00:21:54,764 --> 00:21:56,631
No, we haven't.

374
00:21:56,764 --> 00:21:59,364
Thought so.
Nice to meet you.

375
00:21:59,497 --> 00:22:00,764
I'm Saki.

376
00:22:02,564 --> 00:22:04,431
Uh...

377
00:22:11,231 --> 00:22:13,331
[thinking]
<i>Something ain't right here.</i>

378
00:22:13,464 --> 00:22:15,031
<i>It's no coincidence</i>

379
00:22:15,164 --> 00:22:17,231
<i>that everything's coming</i>
<i>to a head like this.</i>

380
00:22:17,364 --> 00:22:21,431
<i>And there's only one guy</i>
<i>I know who'd be behind it.</i>

381
00:22:21,564 --> 00:22:25,997
Izaya!

382
00:22:47,531 --> 00:22:49,831
♪ [singing in Japanese]

383
00:23:57,531 --> 00:23:59,397
[Chikage] <i>Okay, now,</i>
<i>it's getting complicated.</i>

384
00:23:59,531 --> 00:24:01,797
<i>We've got all these stories</i>
<i>about all these people</i>

385
00:24:01,931 --> 00:24:03,431
<i>crisscrossing</i>
<i>all over the place</i>

386
00:24:03,564 --> 00:24:05,631
<i>like a frickin' spiderweb.</i>

387
00:24:05,764 --> 00:24:07,864
<i>I'm getting in</i>
<i>on the action, too,</i>
<i>'cause, hey, it's what I do.</i>

388
00:24:07,997 --> 00:24:11,631
<i>Next time: In For a Penny,</i>
<i>In For a Pound.</i>

